    <title type="short" as="introduced">Federal Employees' Political Activities Act of 1987</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">A bill to amend title 5, United States Code, to restore to Federal civilian employees their rights to participate voluntarily, as private citizens, in the political processes of the Nation, to protect such employees from improper political solicitations, and for other purposes.</title>
